  </div>
</section>

<section class="code-project">
  <h2>Python Active-subspaces Utility Library</h2>
  <p>A Python library for discovering and exploiting active subspaces in computational models. Provides tools for gradient-based dimension reduction, sufficient summary plots, and response surface construction.</p>
  <div class="project-links">
    <a href="https://github.com/zgrey/active_subspaces">GitHub</a>
